Quin valor es mostra?

??? success "Soluci√≥"
    **4**
    
    | Iteraci√≥ | n | trobat | n mod 2 = 0 | Acci√≥ |
    |----------|---|--------|-------------|-------|
    | 1 | 5 | FALS | 5 mod 2 = 1 ‚úó | n = 4 |
    | 2 | 4 | FALS | 4 mod 2 = 0 ‚úì | trobat = CERT |
    | Fi | 4 | CERT | - | Surt del bucle |

